  - _idx: str_chat_text_3001_5
    _ko: '<color=#d9324e>MewTube</color>를 잘 성장시켜준다면 새로운 거래처를 연결해주겠네.'
    _en: so I’ll let you in on another contact if you can improve <color=#d9324e>MewTube</color> well.
